# No Emojis

Do not use any emoji or emoji-style symbols anywhere in this project.

- In code: no emoji in strings, comments, or log messages.
- In documentation (README, docs, design): no emoji; use plain text, bullets, or ASCII symbols only.
- In commit messages or other project artifacts: no emoji.

Use words or ASCII punctuation instead (e.g. "yes/no", "->", "-", "*").
